   <concept id="FAR_23_105" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">23.105</ph> Exceptions.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The following are excepted from the requirement to procure sustainable products and services:</p>
         <ol id="d1509e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1531e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>  Contracts performed or supplies delivered outside of the United States, unless the agency head determines that such application is in the interest of the United States.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1531e36">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Weapon systems; however, compliance with applicable agency affirmative procurement programs is required for recovered materials per <xref href="23.107-1.dita#FAR_23_107_1"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.107-1</xref> (see <xref href="23.109.dita#FAR_23_109"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.109</xref>(b)) (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title42-section6962&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 6962</xref>) and for alternatives for ozone depleting substances per <xref href="23.107-4.dita#FAR_23_107_4"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.107-4</xref> (see <xref href="23.109.dita#FAR_23_109"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.109</xref>(d)) (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title42-section7671&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 7671l</xref>), unless a written justification exists as described at <xref href="23.104.dita#FAR_23_104"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.104</xref>(a) (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title42-section6962&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 6962(c)(1)</xref> and <xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title7-section8102&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">7 U.S.C. 8102(a)(1)(B)</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1531e41">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Energy-consuming products or systems designed or procured for combat or combat-related missions are not subject to the requirements in <xref href="23.107-3.dita#FAR_23_107_3"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.107-3</xref> (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title42-section8259&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 8259b(a)(5)</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1529e61">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> Biobased products to be used in military equipment (products or systems designed or procured for combat or combat-related missions), spacecraft systems, or launch support equipment are not subject to the requirements in <xref href="23.107-2.dita#FAR_23_107_2"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.107-2</xref> (<xref href="https://www.ecfr.gov/current/title-7/section-3201.3#p-3201.3(e)"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">7 CFR 3201.3(e)</xref>).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
